Interface RemoteRunner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Evaluator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EstimateEvaluator, EvaluatorAbstract, EvaluatorWrapper, ExecuteEvaluator, RecommendEvaluator

    public interface RemoteRunner
extends java.rmi.Remote
    This interface specifies that any object that implements it can start, pause, resume, and stop remotely.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
